After investigation, the washing horse town government on behalf of the Labor company isolation fees is true, the behavior is wrong, the money has been returned, and to the Deputy Mayor Ma removed from office processing.



In response to the quarantine fee imposed on the villagers who returned to their villages to assist the construction of Mount Vulcan, the Xishui County COVID-19 pneumonia epidemic prevention and control headquarters issued a "fact sheet" on March 7,2020, stating that the situation was true and the money had been returned to the Labor Service Company. In addition, after a study and decision by the Xishui County County Party Committee, Comrade Ma Jinan, the deputy mayor of the town of Zima, who is in charge of the work of the isolation point, will be removed from his post.

Recently, a signed Government of the People's Republic of China Document for the town of Zima in Xishui County, Hubei Province has attracted attention. According to the certificate, two workers who assisted in the construction of the Mount Vulcan today received 4200 yuan 150 yuan per day per person. This money is collected by the town government and used to pay the isolation fee in the hotel.

A classmate, surnamed Wang, took him and three other workers from his hometown in Xishui County to the construction site of the Huoshenshan Hospital on January 31, he said in an interview with upstream news. The five of them glued the bathroom fixtures, working a total of three day and three night shifts. After completing their work, the other three workers returned to Xishui County on February 9 and were quarantined in a hotel. Because he has a house in Wuhan, he and CEN will stay in Wuhan Isolation.

On February 21, Wang and CEN returned to the town of Zima in Xishui County, where they were arranged to stay in a "see you later" hotel. On March 4, the town official on duty at the hotel informed him that isolation fees would be charged at the rate of 200 yuan per day. Even though Wang repeatedly told town officials that he was the aid worker, and the headquarters of Huanggang's new crown pneumonia epidemic prevention and control said it was okay not to pay, officials in charge of the town of Washing Ma insisted that they pay the quarantine fee.

On March 6, according to a certificate issued by a netizen, the certificate issued by the town of Xima, Xishui County, Huanggang, Hubei Province, said: "today, two people, including CEN, the construction worker of the Mount Vulcan, returned to the central isolation fee for a total of 4200,150 yuan per day. The money was collected by the town government and transferred directly to the account of the Rural Accounting Service Center of the Finance Office of Zima town, Xishui County, by Wuhan Jinrunshijia Construction and Labor Co. , Ltd. . It was used to pay for the isolation expenses of CEN and Wang in the Bububububububusan hotel."

The certificate immediately attracted attention on the Internet, after the construction of the Fire God mountain back home concentrated isolation, should pay their own isolation fee has also triggered heated debate among netizens.

On March 7, according to a fact sheet issued by the Xishui County COVID-19's pneumonia prevention and control command, after the incident, the Xishui County County Party Committee and the county government quickly set up a joint investigation team consisting of the County Disciplinary Committee, the County Party Committee Publicity Department, and the county public security bureau. After investigation, the situation of the government of Zima town collecting the isolation fees from the Labor Service Company is true and wrong. It reflects the LAX and inaccurate policies and practices of epidemic prevention and control in Xishui County, and the deep sense of remorse and guilt. The fee was returned to the Labor Service Company on the morning of March 7 and an apology was made.

According to the information note, Cen and Wang returned from Wuhan on February 21, in accordance with the relevant requirements of the epidemic prevention and control, two people back to the county, arranged to "see you do not go" hotel focus isolation point isolation for 14 days. During their participation in the construction, China Construction Third Bureau has already paid relevant remuneration according to the National Statutory holiday wage standard. At the same time, China Construction Third Bureau in accordance with the standard of 300 yuan per person per day, the isolation subsidy costs, according to 15 days, a total of 4500 yuan per person.

During the period of isolation, the town of Zima collected the expenses of food and lodging for the isolation period according to the standard of 150 yuan per person per day. The total charge was 4,200 yuan, and the other expenses were borne by the town government, the fee is paid by Wuhan Jinrun Shijia Construction Service Co. , Ltd. directly to the accounting service center of Zima town.

"information note" also said that in-depth lessons learned from the incident, draw inferences from the past, to further identify weaknesses and deficiencies in the work. After investigation, the other county to participate in the construction of Wuhan "two mountains" hospital home quarantine personnel, there is no charge to individuals. Other responsible persons in the town of Zima will be seriously dealt with in accordance with the law and discipline in accordance with the investigation.
